title: R'Bonney Gabriel
summary: R'Bonney Nola Gabriel (English:  AR-bən-ee GAY-bree-əl; Tagalog: [ˈarʔbɔnɪ gɐˈbɾjɛl]; born March 20, 1994) is an American fashion designer, model, and beauty queen who was crowned Miss Universe 2022, becoming the ninth delegate from the United States to win the title, as well as the oldest entrant to be crowned, surpassing Andrea Meza of Mexico. Gabriel was previously crowned as Miss USA 2022.
